      "span_text": "For the traditional screening method, colonies of K. vulgare were selected randomly, then inoculated with B. megaterium 2980 in 250-mL flasks containing 20 mL of the fermentation medium, and incubated at 29 • C for 38 h. [CITATION_1]"
